9-**Tech Stack:** TypeScript 5.7+, Vitest 3, ESLint 9, Node 18+ (the project's `package.json:engines`). All new code follows the project's existing ESM + Node16 module-resolution conventions.
10-
11:**Spec sections referenced throughout:** ┬¦-numbered references in this plan map 1:1 to sections in `2026-04-26-session-recording-and-replay-design.md`.
12-
13-**Branch strategy:** All work on a single chained branch `agent/session-recording`, one commit per Task. Branch stays at the tip awaiting explicit user merge authorization per AGENTS.md. **Per-task multi-CLI review** lands before each commit (see "Per-task review pattern" below) ŌĆö this is mandatory per AGENTS.md, not optional.
