5:**Scope:** Engine-level primitives only (Scope B from brainstorming). Game-side annotation UI, standalone viewer, synthetic playtest harness, counterfactual replay, and strict-mode determinism enforcement are explicitly out of scope and tracked in `docs/design/ai-first-dev-roadmap.md`.
