676-- **Scenario integration.** Convert an existing scenario test (e.g. one of the existing `runScenario(...)` tests) to also assert `scenarioResultToBundle(result)` produces a valid bundle with one `kind: 'assertion'` marker per `result.checks` outcome, matching `outcome.passed` and `outcome.failure`.
677-- **Long capture smoke.** 10000-tick session with 50 commands per tick, default snapshot cadence (10 snapshots), `MemorySink`. Assert bundle loads, `selfCheck()` passes, `openAt` for any tick completes within reasonable time. Throughput target: `openAt()` walking a single segment runs Ōēź 5x recording throughput; `selfCheck()` over N segments scales linearly. Drop the conflated multiplier.
678:- **Cross-snapshot replay.** `openAt(tick)` where `tick` falls between two snapshots ŌĆö verify the replayer correctly walks from the prior snapshot through recorded commands.
